// std/pack.lyx - Binary Serialization/Deserialization
// High-performance binary format for Lyx data structures
// 
// Binary Format:
// - int8:  1 byte
// - int16: 2 bytes (little-endian)
// - int32: 4 bytes (little-endian)
// - int64: 8 bytes (little-endian)
// - float32: 4 bytes IEEE 754
// - float64: 8 bytes IEEE 754
// - bool: 1 byte (0 or 1)
// - string: varint length + UTF-8 bytes
// - array: varint count + elements
// - null: 1 byte (0xFF)

